<Layout darkContent={true} title="用n8n替代本地Cron：情报管线迁移的完整思路 - Lysander" description="从发现定时任务职责重叠，到系统性清理冗余，再到确立迁移后的单一真相源">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <time class="text-white/40 text-sm">2026-04-27</time>
